7. Nf3 {[%cal Gf3e5]} e6 ( { Black can also try } 7...f6!? 8.O-O e6 { , and if } 9.Nh4 { then } 9...Bg4 { saves the bishop. The text move 7...e6 is simpler because it will transpose to one of the mainlines. } ) 
