13. a3 {[%cal Ga3b4]} { Covering the b4-square. } Be7 {[%cal Gd8b6][%csl Gd4]} { Protecting against Bxf6 as preparation for ...Qb6, with annoying pressure on d4 and on the queenside in general. Black has a good position. } 
