12. cxd5 ( 12.Nxd5 { leads back to the game. } ) ( 12.Qxb7 { is met by } 12...Na5 13.Qb4 Rb8 14.Qa3 Nxc4 { and Black regains the pawn with good play. } ) Na5 {[%csl Gb3]} { Kicking the queen away so Black can regain the d5-pawn. } 
