16. Re1! Kf8 
17. Qxe7+ { Everything is forced. } Qxe7 
18. Rxe7 Kxe7 
19. Bxb7 Rad8 
20. Ke2! {[%csl Gd2]} { That is why the king should be on f1! It protects d2 just in time. } Rd6 { The ending is balanced. White has two pawns for the exchange, but Black has active rooks. } 
